scenes.description: Amelia discusses "skanking" and performs a dance, leading into announcements.
Amelia teases upcoming announcements and merchandise.
Showcase of the "Private Investigator Cap" merchandise.
Amelia thanks the audience and introduces a surprise guest.
Amelia and Haachama perform the song "More One Night".
